name: Laser Cut Personalised Heart, Flower and Star Congratulations/Engagement/Wedding Card
description:
Laser Cut Personalised Heart, Flower and Star Congratulations/Engagement/Wedding Card

This listing is for 1 personalised Congratulations card. The card is cut on 240gsm card and comes with a slip insert in the colour of your choice. 

You May choice from: Pink, Blue, Yellow, Red, Green, Lilic, Pastel Blue, Pastel Green, Pastel Yellow

The card also has matching diamante detail. Comes complete with a white envelope. Perfect for that any special occasion.

Each card may vary slightly as each card is individually hand-made and cut. Making this card even more unique.

Size Of Card
Size - 135x135mm

I will email you after payment to confirm what details you would like on the front of your card. You may want to include: 

Congratulations with the couples name (like the image shown) or Congrats On Your Engagement. In fact the choice is yours, you may personalises the card with your own words.

As this card is personalised, it will be posted in 3-5 days after I have received all the details. If you need this item quicker contact me and I will let you know whether it would be possible.

Packaged in a cellobag to protect the item. 
Posted via First Class Post.

Thanks for looking!
